{"tid":1012622,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"華航機師工會突襲 今早6時啟動罷工","createTime":"2019-02-07T17:12:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T18:03:26.000Z","uid":38376,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"26d28a66407f1be68314d578df0af38589e1025d","tid":1012622,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190208/59234163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234163&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=c261c836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234163&h=d17f1eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190208/59234163</a><br />\n<br />\n華航勞資談判破裂。機師工會華航分會宣佈，今日清晨6時開始罷工，預計有700名機師配合，目前正值春節高峯期，機師工會發動罷工，預計會造成旅客嚴重延誤。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家多d留意下，華航已經罷工好多次"},{"pid":"de11023a948798eab17f17abe3a6493488d917ce","tid":1012622,"uid":60000,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"26d28a66407f1be68314d578df0af38589e1025d","tid":1012622,"uid":38376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T17:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190208/59234163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234163&d=HNFwsad0YdNlvWXbC%2BF%2BcrccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=c261c836\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190208%2F59234163&h=d17f1eb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190208/59234163</a><br />\n<br />\n華航勞資談判破裂。機師工會華航分會宣佈，今日清晨6時開始罷工，預計有700名機師配合，目前正值春節高峯期，機師工會發動罷工，預計會造成旅客嚴重延誤。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />